{"tid":1366764,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"727元朗反黑 衝突唔再係主軸","createTime":"2019-07-26T05:05:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T06:40:16.000Z","uid":34626,"like":30,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3ccea507527f05066bfb39e2ba960292b21b17ab","tid":1366764,"uid":34626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T05:05:33.000Z","msg":"街頭衝突嘅目的無非係表達不滿<br />\n但呢一刻<span style=\"color: red;\">連建制陣營都開始分裂</span>嘅時候 <br />\n體制入面個個都想同林鄭何妖割𥱊<br />\n我地727真係唔需要挑起更多矛盾比人分散721惡行<br />\n<br />\n其實你睇下藍絲啲文宣就知<br />\n無論係721定727都話<span style=\"color: red;\">示威者想入去搞事</span><br />\n如果主動入村衝突 咪應驗左佢地講嘅野<br />\n<br />\n721 727 矛頭亦都會由 <br />\n<strong>警黑合作</strong> 變成 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">兩派衝突</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n727 好簡單 入去 叫口號又好 派膠又好 唔洗起衝突<br />\n白衫搞事 記得影低 叫記者黎 <br />\n衛隊一定要有 但冇需要主動搞佢地<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">否定佢地所講 我地出現為左搞事嘅講法</span><br />\n又最能夠表達我地對反黑嘅訴求<br />\n<br />\n我不嬲覺得我地唔洗贏港豬嘅輿論 抗爭唔需要底線<br />\n我都好嬲 好想覆桌 但真係要睇大局 <br />\n<br />\n但你睇總商會都出聲明就知<br />\n宜家講緊可以<span style=\"color: orange;\">贏倒體制入面嘅支持</span><br />\n721 727 將會係一個好大嘅<span style=\"color: red;\">轉捩點</span><br />\n爭取最大嘅政治能量去抗爭<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命！"},{"pid":"50012691eb861983064d0572440c0403a46c0377","tid":1366764,"uid":34626,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T05:07:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TfE4DnfVj-Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DTfE4DnfVj-Q&d=AixoiqhHuTrv0%2F0Xa%2FX9x7XdyKWV89KwSxbYnQ5zRIM%3D&h=9ee19cc2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TfE4DnfVj-Q</a><br />\n<br />\n唔想睇曬嘅話 43:10開始睇"},{"pid":"33318de0761f604c48abefe18f9b64fc040531d9","tid":1366764,"uid":34626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T05:08:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eb73a3f375afffb12fa5b7556279c3b244ba2f77","tid":1366764,"uid":34626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T05:11:06.000Z","msg":"推"}